  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN US ON DISCORD!</h1><p><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://discordapp.com/invite/7s4Kw4V\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  ><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1001870/extras/Discord.png?t=1554908871\" ></a></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>RoboVirus is a 2 to 4 player local multiplayer game where you can have a blast with your friends. Kill each other in chaotic surroundings using rockets, lasers, or the environment.<br><br>The game scenery is located in an Utopia gone bad megastructure RobotHive, where the motherboard has gone bad because of the RoboVirus. The players are thrown into the arena by the corrupted motherboard in a fight against death in an evolving arena!<br><br>RoboVirus is developed by Stolen Shoes Entertainment, a small indie game studio located in central Finland. We like to play games, make games and go to sauna!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dash</h2>Use dash to get closer to your friends and drop them dead or escape deadly projectiles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1001870/extras/GIF-Dash-2.gif?t=1554908871\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Maps</h2>Play trough interactive maps avoiding obstacles, at the moment we have three interactive maps and one stationary normal map.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1001870/extras/GIF-Maps-2.gif?t=1554908871\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Local play for up to 4 players<br></li><li> 3 Interactive levels<br></li><li> 5 Overpowered weapons<br></li><li> Full Xbox controller support<br></li><li> Single-player with bots</li></ul>",
